  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Backpacks
    Team Based: Yourself and a partner have a virtual 'backpack' to store your items in.
    Backpacks.Backpack
    Represents a theoretical backpack within the game
    Barebones  
    Bowless
    Bows are not craftable and skeletons are kept from dropping them
    Cutclean
    Anything that drops a smeltable/cookable item has already had that done to it.
    Diamondless
    Diamond ore no longer drops diamonds, and players (when killed by another player) drop a diamond.
    Fireless
    You may not take damage from anything fire related.
    Goldless
    The ability to mine gold pieces is stripped, and you may only obtain them via killing a player; which now drops one!
    Horseless
    Disallows the taming and riding of horses.
    Rodless
    Prevent the crafting of fishing rods

    Timebomb
